subjects = ["toan", "ngu_van", "ngoai_ngu", "vat_li", "hoa_hoc", "sinh_hoc", "lich_su", "dia_li", "gdcd"]

# To DataFrame mi vi im theo tng khong
df_10 = df[subjects].applymap(lambda x: 1 if x == 10 else 0)
df_kha = df[subjects].applymap(lambda x: 1 if 8 <= x < 10 else 0)
df_trung_binh = df[subjects].applymap(lambda x: 1 if 5 <= x < 8 else 0)
df_duoi_tb = df[subjects].applymap(lambda x: 1 if 2.5 <= x < 5 else 0)
df_liet = df[subjects].applymap(lambda x: 1 if x < 2.5 else 0)
df_0 = df[subjects].applymap(lambda x: 1 if x == 0 else 0)

# m s lng im theo tng khong
num_10 = df_10.sum().sum()
num_kha = df_kha.sum().sum()
num_trung_binh = df_trung_binh.sum().sum()
num_duoi_tb = df_duoi_tb.sum().sum()
num_liet = df_liet.sum().sum()
num_0 = df_0.sum().sum()

# To DataFrame mi cho d liu s lng im
data = {
    "Loi im": ["10", "Kh", "Trung bnh", "Di trung bnh", "Lit", "0"],
    "S lng im": [num_10, num_kha, num_trung_binh, num_duoi_tb, num_liet, num_0]
}

# Phn loi im
def classify_score(score):
    if score == 10:
        return "10"
    elif 8 <= score < 10:
        return "Kh"
    elif 5 <= score < 8:
        return "TB"
    elif 2.5 <= score < 5:
        return "Di TB"
    elif score < 2.5:
        return "Lit"
    else:
        return "0"

# p dng hm phn loi im vo cc ct mn hc
df['toan'] = df['toan'].apply(classify_score)
df['ngu_van'] = df['ngu_van'].apply(classify_score)
df['ngoai_ngu'] = df['ngoai_ngu'].apply(classify_score)
df['vat_li'] = df['vat_li'].apply(classify_score)
df['hoa_hoc'] = df['hoa_hoc'].apply(classify_score)
df['sinh_hoc'] = df['sinh_hoc'].apply(classify_score)
df['lich_su'] = df['lich_su'].apply(classify_score)
df['dia_li'] = df['dia_li'].apply(classify_score)
df['gdcd'] = df['gdcd'].apply(classify_score)

# To figure v cc subplot
fig, axes = plt.subplots(nrows=3, ncols=3, figsize=(15, 10))
fig.suptitle('Phn loi im theo mn hc', fontsize=16)

# Biu  cho tng mn hc
df['toan'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', ax=axes[0, 0], title='Ton')
df['ngu_van'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', ax=axes[0, 1], title='Ng Vn')
df['ngoai_ngu'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', ax=axes[0, 2], title='Ngoi Ng')
df['vat_li'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', ax=axes[1, 0], title='Vt L')
df['hoa_hoc'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', ax=axes[1, 1], title='Ha Hc')
df['sinh_hoc'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', ax=axes[1, 2], title='Sinh Hc')
df['lich_su'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', ax=axes[2, 0], title='Lch S')
df['dia_li'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', ax=axes[2, 1], title='a L')
df['gdcd'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar', ax=axes[2, 2], title='GDCD')

# Tinh chnh khong cch gia cc subplot
plt.tight_layout(rect=[0, 0.03, 1, 0.95])
plt.show()

# Tnh phn trm phn loi im
def calculate_percentage(data):
    total = len(data)
    percentages = data.value_counts(normalize=True) * 100
    return percentages

# To figure v cc subplot
fig, axes = plt.subplots(nrows=3, ncols=3, figsize=(15, 10))
fig.suptitle('Phn trm phn loi im theo mn hc', fontsize=16)

# Biu  pie cho tng mn hc
calculate_percentage(df['toan']).plot(kind='pie', autopct='%1.1f%%', ax=axes[0, 0], title='Ton')
calculate_percentage(df['ngu_van']).plot(kind='pie', autopct='%1.1f%%', ax=axes[0, 1], title='Ng Vn')
calculate_percentage(df['ngoai_ngu']).plot(kind='pie', autopct='%1.1f%%', ax=axes[0, 2], title='Ngoi Ng')
calculate_percentage(df['vat_li']).plot(kind='pie', autopct='%1.1f%%', ax=axes[1, 0], title='Vt L')
calculate_percentage(df['hoa_hoc']).plot(kind='pie', autopct='%1.1f%%', ax=axes[1, 1], title='Ha Hc')
calculate_percentage(df['sinh_hoc']).plot(kind='pie', autopct='%1.1f%%', ax=axes[1, 2], title='Sinh Hc')
calculate_percentage(df['lich_su']).plot(kind='pie', autopct='%1.1f%%', ax=axes[2, 0], title='Lch S')
calculate_percentage(df['dia_li']).plot(kind='pie', autopct='%1.1f%%', ax=axes[2, 1], title='a L')
calculate_percentage(df['gdcd']).plot(kind='pie', autopct='%1.1f%%', ax=axes[2, 2], title='GDCD')

# Tinh chnh khong cch gia cc subplot
plt.tight_layout(rect=[0, 0.03, 1, 0.95])

# Hin th biu 
plt.show()
